// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

export interface TodayEnergyData {
  /** ç»¼åˆèƒ½é‡åˆ†æ•° (0-100) */
  overallScore?: number;
  /** èƒ½é‡ç­‰çº§æ ‡ç­¾ */
  energyLabel?: string;
  /** å…«å­—ä»Šæ—¥è¿åŠ¿ */
  baziInsight?: {
    score?: number;
    headline?: string;
    tip?: string;
  };
  /** å æ˜Ÿä»Šæ—¥èƒ½é‡ */
  zodiacInsight?: {
    score?: number;
    headline?: string;
    tip?: string;
  };
  /** ç»¼åˆè¡ŒåŠ¨å»ºè®® */
  actionTip?: string;
  /** ä»Šæ—¥å…³é”®è¯ */
  keywords?: string[];
  /** é—®å€™è¯­ */
  greeting?: string;
  /** å½“å‰èŠ‚æ°” */
  solarTerm?: string;
}

export interface TodayEnergyCardProps {
  data?: TodayEnergyData | null;
  displayName?: string;
  onClick?: () => void;
  className?: string;
}

// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
// Helper: Energy Level Config
// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

function getEnergyConfig(score: number): {
  label: string;
  emoji: string;
  gradient: string;
  textColor: string;
  bgColor: string;
} {
  if (score >= 80) {
    return {
      label: "èƒ½é‡å……æ²›",
      emoji: "ğŸŒŸ",
      gradient: "from-amber-400 to-orange-500",
      textColor: "text-amber-700",
      bgColor: "bg-amber-50",
    };
  } else if (score >= 60) {
    return {
      label: "çŠ¶æ€è‰¯å¥½",
      emoji: "âœ¨",
      gradient: "from-green-400 to-emerald-500",
      textColor: "text-green-700",
      bgColor: "bg-green-50",
    };
  } else if (score >= 40) {
    return {
      label: "å¹³ç¨³è¿è¡Œ",
      emoji: "ğŸŒ™",
      gradient: "from-blue-400 to-indigo-500",
      textColor: "text-blue-700",
      bgColor: "bg-blue-50",
    };
  } else {
    return {
      label: "éœ€è¦ä¼‘æ¯",
      emoji: "ğŸŒ¿",
      gradient: "from-slate-400 to-gray-500",
      textColor: "text-slate-700",
      bgColor: "bg-slate-50",
    };
  }
}

// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
// Sub-components
// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

function EnergyMeter({ score, label }: { score: number; label: string }) {
  const config = getEnergyConfig(score);

  return (
    <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
      {/* Score Circle */}
      <div className="relative">
        <div
          className={cn(
            "w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center",
            "bg-gradient-to-br",
            config.gradient,
            "shadow-lg"
          )}
          style={{
            boxShadow: `0 4px 20px rgba(234, 190, 138, 0.3)`,
          }}
        >
          <span className="text-2xl font-bold text-white">{score}</span>
        </div>
        {/* Decorative ring */}
        <div
          className="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-2 border-white/30 animate-pulse"
          style={{ animationDuration: "3s" }}
        />
      </div>

      {/* Label */}
      <div>
        <p className="text-xs text-text-tertiary">ç»¼åˆèƒ½é‡</p>
        <p className={cn("text-lg font-semibold", config.textColor)}>{label}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

function InsightRow({
  icon,
  skillId,
  label,
  score,
  headline,
}: {
  icon?: React.ReactNode;
  skillId?: string;
  label: string;
  score?: number;
  headline?: string;
}) {
  return (
    <div className="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/50">
      {/* Icon */}
      {skillId ? (
        <SkillIcon skillId={skillId} size="sm" glow={false} />
      ) : (
        <div className="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vellum-100 flex items-center justify-center">
          {icon}
        </div>
      )}

      {/* Content */}
      <div className="flex-1 min-w-0">
        <div className="flex items-center gap-2 mb-0.5">
          <span className="text-xs text-text-tertiary">{label}</span>
          {score !== undefined && (
            <span className="text-xs font-medium text-accent-primary">
              {score}%
            </span>
          )}
        </div>
        {headline && (
          <p className="text-sm text-text-primary leading-snug line-clamp-2">
            {headline}
          </p>
        )}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
// Main Component
// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

export function TodayEnergyCard({
  data,
  displayName,
  onClick,
  className,
}: TodayEnergyCardProps) {
  // Default values
  const overallScore = data?.overallScore ?? 75;
  const energyLabel = data?.energyLabel ?? getEnergyConfig(overallScore).label;
  const config = getEnergyConfig(overallScore);

  // Generate greeting based on time
  const getTimeGreeting = () => {
    const hour = new Date().getHours();
    if (hour < 6) return "å¤œæ·±äº†";
    if (hour < 12) return "æ—©ä¸Šå¥½";
    if (hour < 18) return "ä¸‹åˆå¥½";
    return "æ™šä¸Šå¥½";
  };

  const greeting = data?.greeting || getTimeGreeting();
  const fullGreeting = displayName ? `${greeting}ï¼Œ${displayName}` : greeting;

  // Empty state - show a warm welcome
  if (!data) {
    return (
      <div
        onClick={onClick}
        className={cn(
          "relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl cursor-pointer",
          "bg-gradient-to-br from-vellum-50 via-gold-50/50 to-mystic-50/30",
          "border border-vellum-200/50",
          "shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover",
          "transition-all duration-300",
          "p-5",
          className
        )}
      >
        {/* Background decoration */}
        <div className="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-bl from-gold-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-2xl" />

        <div className="relative">
          {/* Header */}
          <div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <GradientEmojiIcon emoji="âœ¨" theme="gold" size="md" glow />
            <div>
              <p className="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">
                {fullGreeting}
              </p>
              <p className="text-sm text-text-secondary">
                å¼€å§‹å¯¹è¯ï¼Œäº†è§£ä»Šæ—¥èƒ½é‡
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* CTA */}
          <div className="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-accent-primary/10 hover:bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
            <Sparkles className="w-4 h-4" />
            <span>å¼€å¯ä»Šæ—¥æ¢ç´¢</span>
            <ChevronRight className="w-4 h-4" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    );
  }

  return (
    <div
      onClick={onClick}
      className={cn(
        "relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl cursor-pointer",
        "bg-gradient-to-br from-vellum-50 via-gold-50/50 to-mystic-50/30",
        "border border-vellum-200/50",
        "shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover",
        "transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.01]",
        "p-5",
        className
      )}
    >
      {/* Decorative background elements */}
      <div className="absolute top-0 right-0 w-40 h-40 bg-gradient-to-bl from-gold-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl" />
      <div className="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-tr from-mystic-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-2xl" />

      <div className="relative">
        {/* Header with greeting */}
        <div className="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
            <GradientEmojiIcon emoji={config.emoji} theme="gold" size="md" glow />
            <div>
              <p className="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">
                {fullGreeting}
              </p>
              {data.solarTerm && (
                <p className="text-xs text-text-tertiary">
                  {data.solarTerm} Â· ä»Šæ—¥èƒ½é‡æŠ¥å‘Š
                </p>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Today's date */}
          <div className="text-right">
            <p className="text-xs text-text-tertiary">
              {new Date().toLocaleDateString("zh-CN", {
                month: "long",
                day: "numeric",
              })}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Energy Meter */}
        <div className="mb-5">
          <EnergyMeter score={overallScore} label={energyLabel} />
        </div>

        {/* Insight Rows */}
        <div className="space-y-2 mb-4">
          {data.baziInsight && (
            <InsightRow
              skillId="bazi"
              label="å…«å­—"
              score={data.baziInsight.score}
              headline={data.baziInsight.headline || data.baziInsight.tip}
            />
          )}

          {data.zodiacInsight && (
            <InsightRow
              skillId="zodiac"
              label="å æ˜Ÿ"
              score={data.zodiacInsight.score}
              headline={data.zodiacInsight.headline || data.zodiacInsight.tip}
            />
          )}
        </div>

        {/* Action Tip */}
        {data.actionTip && (
          <div className="p-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50/80 to-orange-50/60 border border-amber-200/30">
            <div className="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span className="text-base">ğŸ’¡</span>
              <div>
                <p className="text-xs font-medium text-amber-700 mb-0.5">
                  ä»Šæ—¥å»ºè®®
                </p>
                <p className="text-sm text-ink-700">{data.actionTip}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        )}

        {/* Keywords */}
        {data.keywords && data.keywords.length > 0 && (
          <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            {data.keywords.map((keyword, index) => (
              <span
                key={index}
                className="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-white/60 text-text-secondary border border-white/50"
              >
                {keyword}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        )}

        {/* Explore More */}
        <div className="flex items-center justify-end gap-1 mt-4 text-accent-primary">
          <span className="text-xs">æŸ¥çœ‹è¯¦æƒ…</span>
          <ChevronRight className="w-4 h-4" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
// Skeleton
// â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

export function TodayEnergyCardSkeleton({ className }: { className?: string }) {
  return (
    <div
      className={cn(
        "relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl",
        "bg-gradient-to-br from-vellum-50 via-gold-50/50 to-mystic-50/30",
        "border border-vellum-200/50",
